{"tid":1669502,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"對付干預學術自由既城大Marketing TAN Yong Chin 既另類方法(長文慎入)","createTime":"2019-10-22T14:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T10:09:23.000Z","uid":89937,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fef0e0c4cf2dc42fd5189b8b6eafbc15170b1f9f","tid":1669502,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJtwSy8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJtwSy8.jpg&h=2227c649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YbqGvkP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYbqGvkP.jpg&h=82973787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果吉野家等N間公司都因為政治問題o係 digital marketing出事<br />\n你用呢個態度叫人唔好講政治，本來就係worst example<br />\n唔好講D咩陳義較高既學術自由同學者風骨<br />\n教marketing 無marketing觸角，真係一個天大笑話<br />\n<br />\n但呢單野城大唔會郁佢(除非搞到勁大獲)<br />\n然後結果只係罰佢唔教書，但對佢黎講可能係求仁得仁<br />\n因為依家既佢一定係Chur Research 唔想教書<br />\n<br />\n所以識玩既可以o係班學術期刊既Editor面前唱佢<br />\n幫佢出名，教digital marketing唔識marketing 自己製造自己既負面例子(<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點！</span></strong>因為學者可能對香港問題偏保守，但亦要有心理準備人地唔應機。)<br />\n等佢以後出稿都難(6年後要上副教授時就GG)<br />\n大家可以留意番呢幾本<br />\n<br />\nMarketing Science: <a href=\"https://pubsonline.informs.org/journal/mksc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubsonline.informs.org%2Fjournal%2Fmksc&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU4429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=059b68fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubsonline.informs.org/journal/mksc</a><br />\nJournal of Marketing :<a href=\"https://www.ama.org/journal-of-marketing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ama.org%2Fjournal-of-marketing%2F&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU4429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=476336f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ama.org/journal-of-marketing/</a><br />\nJournal of Marketing Research: <a href=\"https://www.ama.org/journal-of-marketing-research/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=